graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% External Dependencies (Required Platform)
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
    Dashboard -->|cluster API| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    Dashboard -.->|metrics optional| Prometheus[Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS]

    %% External Tech Stack
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 20.x]
    Dashboard -->|UI framework| React[React 18.2.0]
    Dashboard -->|components| PatternFly[PatternFly 6.3.1]
    Dashboard -->|backend| Fastify[Fastify 4.28.1]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient[Kubernetes client-node library]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|platform config| OdhOperator[OpenDataHub Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster, DSCInitialization]
    Dashboard -->|create/manage| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Jupyter environments]
    Dashboard -->|status display| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService]
    Dashboard -->|create/manage| ModelRegistry[Model Registry Operator<br/>ModelRegistry CR]
    Dashboard -->|serving config| OdhModelController[ODH Model Controller<br/>ServingRuntimes]
    Dashboard -->|workbench mgmt| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Notebook instances]
    Dashboard -->|pipeline integration| DSP[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Runs, Experiments]
    Dashboard -->|bias metrics| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service<br/>Metrics display]
    Dashboard -->|workload queues| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Queue configs]
    Dashboard -->|distributed training| CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>Training workloads]
    Dashboard -->|LLM inference| LlamaStack[LlamaStack<br/>Distributions]
    Dashboard -.->|traffic mgmt| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Istio<br/>mTLS optional]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|console links| OpenShiftConsole[OpenShift Console<br/>Navigation]
    Dashboard -.->|analytics optional| Segment[Segment Analytics<br/>Usage tracking]
    Dashboard -.->|documentation| ExternalDocs[External Documentation<br/>Content URLs]

